data.bio:
Test Lawyer is a business/corporate lawyer and founder of Indigo Venture Law Offices, an innovative law firm committed to providing “high value legal solutions” for small businesses on a fixed fee basis.  With more than 25 years experience, Test has a passion for helping entrepreneurs and business owners by turning complex legal matters into practical solutions. He is passionate about changing the way law is practiced in the USA--he believes strongly that every business owner, regardless of the size of his company should enjoy full legal protection and that legal documents protecting business owners should be affordable, accessible and comprehensible. Test has over 25 years of experience as an attorney. He is co-founder of Indigo Venture Law Offices , and founder of LEXpertise.com. 

Test started out as an entrepreneur working “in the trenches” as President of a software development company and then part of the management team of two venture-backed startups providing Internet related products and services, each of which raised over $20 million of capital.  In 2002, he started a solo practice, which later became Indigo Venture Law Offices.

Indigo Venture Law Offices provides legal counsel to traditional and web-based businesses throughout the business lifecycle - start-up, growth, and succession - with services that include incorporation, LLC formation, financing, mergers, acquisitions, employment, compensation (including equity incentive compensation), sales and distribution agreements, software and technology licensing, ecommerce, and Internet-related issues. 

With offices in Cambridge, MA and Louisville, CO, the firm offers a unique “solutions approach” to the practice of law. Our Venture Attorneys start by getting to know each client and understanding their business before applying our legal skills. The firm has pioneered the concepts for a new client-oriented business model by offering Legal Strategy Sessions, Three Levels of Service and Unmetered Consultations. For more information about Indigo Venture Law Offices, visit our web site at www.ivlo.com.

Test is admitted to practice law in Colorado and Massachusetts.  For a full bio, go to http://www.indigoventure.com/attorneys/rglovsky.html.
